    <item>
      <title>税收之争迫在眉睫，白宫淡化提高盐税上限的希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/white-house-downplays-hopes-for-salt-cap-hike-as-tax-fight-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登的首席经济顾问表示，当国会明年辩论是否延长唐纳德·特朗普的减税政策时，纽约州人和加利福尼亚州人寻求大幅扩大州和地方税收减免，但他们的愿望不太可能实现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/white-house-downplays-hopes-for-salt-cap-hike-as-tax-fight-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙支持率跌至 2018 年底以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/macron-approval-rating-falls-to-lowest-since-late-2018-in-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙因在欧洲议会选举中失利而宣布提前投票，随后一项民意调查显示，马克龙的支持率跌至五年半以来的最低水平，这加剧了法国的政治动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/macron-approval-rating-falls-to-lowest-since-late-2018-in-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 14:27:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>也门附近船只在几天内遭遇第二次袭击后起火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/ship-on-fire-near-yemen-after-second-attack-in-as-many-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一艘小型货船在亚丁湾航行时被两枚射弹击中后起火，这是两天内发生的第二起重大事件，也是袭击事件的新一轮升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/ship-on-fire-near-yemen-after-second-attack-in-as-many-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 12:28:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
